headline: PJP: Big Pharma Concentration Risks Amid Looming Confirmation Of RFK Jr.
summary: This article discusses the risk and opportunities of six major constituents of PJP ETF: Pfizer, Amgen, Gilead, AbbVie, BMY, and Merck. Read more here.
